data.description: LOCATION-LOCATION-LOCATION! Come visit this amazing home with easy access to shopping, restaurants and entertainment! This beautiful unit showcases 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a 1-car attached garage plus 1-designated carport space, upstairs laundry, newer roof, gorgeous wood floors on main level, gas fireplace dramatic vaulted ceilings and skylights for tons of natural light! Upon entering this home you'll be treated to the open concept living area with gas fireplace, vaulted ceilings and separate dining room. In the kitchen you'll find a breakfast bar, gas stove and all kitchen appliances included. Upstairs you'll find a conveniently located laundry room with two large bedrooms! This gem won't last long!
